      "court_date": "2010-11-03 9:00 AM",
      "matters": "Petition For Breach Of Trust<br>Off Calendar Nov-03-2010 Text Ruling<br>MINI MINUTES: Appearances: Brian McCaffrey for Sheldon Lim. Daniel Casas for Alan Lim (Petitioner).<br><br>The Court stated that this matter appears to arise out the same Trust in which it had issued an order and asked if Counsel objected to the matters being consolidated. Counsel did not object to consolidation of the matters and stated that discovery needed to be conducted. This action is being consolidated with case number PTR-09-292691. Mr. Casas is to prepare the order indicating the lower case number as the lead case. No further documents are to be filed in case number PTR-10-293878. The Petition for Breach of Trust was continued to January 19, 2011 at 9:00 a.m., in Dept. 204 in the lower case number for status of discovery and for trial setting. <br><br>Judge: Mary E. Wiss. Reporter: Diana Chen, CSR#11312. Clerk: Rosie Noguera. Bailiff: Deputy A. Payne.<br>",
